import {
  StyledForm,
  Wrapper,
  Title,
  Label,
  StyledField,
  Button,
} from './ContactForm.styled';

export const ContactForm = () => {
  return (
    <Wrapper>
      <StyledForm>
        <Label>
          Name
          <StyledField
            type="text"
            name="name"
            title="Name may contain only letters, apostrophe, dash and spaces. For example Adrian, Jacob Mercer, Charles de Batz de Castelmore d'Artagnan"
            placeholder="name"
            required
          />
        </Label>
        <Label>
          Number
          <StyledField type="tel" name="number" placeholder="number" required />
        </Label>
        <Button type="submit">Add number</Button>
      </StyledForm>
    </Wrapper>
  );
};
